[00:16.920]Because a vision softly creeping
[00:16.920]因为一道幻象悄悄来临
[00:22.140]Left its seeds while I was sleeping
[00:22.140]趁我入睡时播下了种子
[00:26.900]And the vision that was planted in my brain
[00:26.900]那在我的脑海中生长的幻象
[00:34.050]Still remains
[00:34.050]仍然滞留
[00:37.370]Within the sound of silence
[00:37.370]在寂静之声中
[00:43.480]In restless dreams I walked alone
[00:43.480]在一次不安的梦境中我独自徘徊
[00:48.470]Narrow streets of cobblestone
[00:48.470]流连于狭窄的卵石道上
[00:53.230]Neath the halo of a street lamp
