[01:02.500]When my eyes were stabbed by the flash of a neon light
[01:02.500]当我察觉眼睛被霓虹灯光刺痛时
[01:09.900]That split the night
[01:09.900]灯光划破夜空
[01:13.310]And touched the sound of silence
[01:13.310]触到那寂静之声
[01:19.210]And in the naked light I saw
[01:19.210]在那无遮蔽的灯光下我看见
[01:24.000]Ten thousand people, maybe more
[01:24.000]成千上万的人们,也许更多
[01:29.000]People talking without speaking
[01:29.000]人们说而不言
[01:34.000]People hearing without listening
[01:34.000]人们听而不闻
[01:38.500]People writing songs that voices never share
[01:38.500]人们谱写从未被吟唱的乐章
[01:47.000]And no one dare disturb the sound of silence
[01:47.000]没有人敢去惊动那寂静之声
[01:57.000]"Fools" said I, "You do not know
[01:57.000]“傻子,你们根本不知道.”我说,
[02:01.500]Silence like a cancer grows"
[02:01.500]“寂静早已犹如癌症一般生长”，
[02:06.630]Hear my words that I might teach you
[02:06.630]细细聆听我教你们的说的话语,
[02:11.300]Take my arms that I might reach you
[02:11.300]紧握我递给你们的手臂.”
[02:16.250]But my words like silent raindrops fell
[02:16.250]但是我的话如同雨滴般无声落下
[02:26.300]And echoed in the wells of silence
[02:26.300]回荡在寂静的深井里
[02:34.140]And the people bowed and prayed to the neon god they made.
[02:34.140]人们朝着他们创造的虚幻的神（霓虹灯）低头祈祷
[02:43.700]And the sign flashed out its warning
[02:43.700]而霓虹灯广告牌却在一闪一闪发出警告,
[02:48.300]And the words that it was forming
[02:48.300]它展现出来的话语是:
[02:53.100]And the sign said:"The words of the prophets are written on the subway walls
